<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>219</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chielna thu chuh gensawn zel un,
 A ut cheng hung thei unau;
 Gensawn un, gensawn un,
 Hehpihna thu vaithak;
 Dangchakte cheng kiengah gensawn un,
 Gensawn un, gensawn un.

[V2]
 Chielna thu chuh gensawn zel un,
 Pathien Thu chuh gensawn un;
 Namtin, chitin, mitin in Krista,
 Thu a het mau chengin;
 Hetna di'n, hetna di'n,
 Lal Krista a het nang un.

[V3]
 2. Lungmuonna khawn chuh thak sawn un,
 Lalpa'n nang A hun piek chuh;
 Thak sawn un, thak sawn un,
 Thagau gimthei leh lung -
 Khamte'n le a dawn theihna dingun,
 Thak sawn un, thak sawn un.

[V4]
 3. Vangsakna, thutiem gensawn un,
 Damsung a na neih ding chuh;
 Gensawn un, gensawn un,
 Mi lungdawngte na panpih thei;
 Lungkhamna laka umte,
 Gensawn un, gensawn un.

[V5]
 4. &quot;Hangsan un&quot; tih thu gensawn un,
 Thimna chuh bei ding ei tai;
 Gensawn un, gensawn un,
 Enin, zing khuo a vak pan tai;
 Manthai theihlohna, gamah,
 Gensawn un, gensawn un.</lyrics>
<title>PASS IT ON</title>
</song>